name: r-vam
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '1.0.0' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-vam
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/VAM_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/VAM/VAM_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 19de5c66034c9ec9ac6d8c8ce216ae951145b66f4b6d482c518935fe49449812

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
    - cross-r-base {{ r_base }}    # [build_platform != target_platform]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-mass
    - r-matrix
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-mass
    - r-matrix

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('VAM')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('VAM')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=VAM
  license: GPL-2.0-or-later
  summary: Contains logic for cell-specific gene set scoring of single cell RNA sequencing data.
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file:
    - '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
